Fractal Project

Objective: To understand methods and method call and how to use them for recursion.

Steps
1. Use recursion to produce a fractal using Java or JavaScript.
2. Present your work.
Grade: 25% Code works. 25% originality (small changes are ok) 50% understanding

****How To Get Started*****
Go through the tutorial quickly to gain some coding skills.
http://www.crunchzilla.com/code-maven

Look at the recursion section.
You may use the tree or fern as a starting point or research other fractals. 
Wikipedia is a good place to find popular fractals.
Your fractal should be implimented in javaScript using the canvas.
